      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIC BANDIT (1) finished well back at Richmond last time when a 6 length eighth (30.16) but back to the course now of her latest success. The form from her last run stacks up well. Key runner on her best form. HEY BUBBA LOUIE (6) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Missed the frame latest (29.87) when fifth over 520m at Richmond in a NG. Looks suited here and can measure up. RELEASE POINT (8) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten one length (29.66) behind Zipping Violet at this track. Will give a great sight again. WONDER I DO (4) is a last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
